text: Aubevoye is a former commune in the Eure department in Normandy in northern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Le Val-d'Hazey.Arrêté préfectoral 17 December 2015 ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Eure department ==References== Category:Former communes of Eure
title: Aubevoye
